Here.

159
00:07:19,795 --> 00:07:21,754
Please complete your
discharge procedure later.

160
00:07:22,194 --> 00:07:23,194
Okay.

161
00:07:24,874 --> 00:07:26,435
What's your name

162
00:07:26,874 --> 00:07:28,115
