191
00:08:29,914 --> 00:08:30,555
Pei.

192
00:08:30,675 --> 00:08:31,194
Yes.

193
00:08:31,194 --> 00:08:33,115
You kept the scissors and paper cutter, right?

194
00:08:34,115 --> 00:08:36,275
Good job. I thank you
on behalf of my parents

195
