for saving their daughter.

196
00:08:41,714 --> 00:08:43,394
Totally unreasonable!

197
00:08:44,514 --> 00:08:45,274
Wei An.

198
00:08:45,435 --> 00:08:46,875
Tell me, why can't I just be
the CEO of Yunma?

199
